<headline>Special Weather Statement issued December 31 at 10:08PM EST  by NWS Detroit</headline>
<description>...Some Icy Spots Possible on the Roads...
Areas of light rain and drizzle this evening will diminish
overnight. However, temperatures will drop below freezing
overnight. This will open the door for the development of some
black ice on untreated surfaces. Drivers should exercise caution
on area roads tonight.</description>
